{
  "_comment": "Framework fingerprints. Order matters only for tie-breaking display; matching is score-based. classRegex entries are .NET regex evaluated against the HWND class name (and the UIA element ClassName) with IgnoreCase. modules entries are matched by case-insensitive equality against module file names (e.g. 'PresentationCore.dll' must match exactly, not as a substring).",
