    {
      "_comment": "RNW shares HWND classes with vanilla WinUI 3 (WinUIDesktopWin32WindowClass, DesktopChildSiteBridge). We deliberately set NO class regex here so class-only classification correctly returns 'WinUI 3' for those HWNDs; RNW is differentiated by its loaded modules only and wins the full classifier when 5+ of its modules are loaded (since each module = +1, beating WinUI 3's +4 class match).",
